text: IT's been 11 YEARS NOW, BUT EXO'S VOCALS ARE STILL THE BEST AND MOST SOULFUL I've ever heard IN THE ENTIRE K-POP INDUSTRY. And no, it's not an exaggeration or bias, it's THE PURE TRUTH.

text:
Once again, I am convinced that EXO is the biggest diamond, not only in the entire history 
of sm, but in the entire history of the K-POP industry. It's been 11 years, but I haven't seen

author: @liza_pet
text: 11 years have passed, but I have said and will say EXO is a real diamond not only of SM but of the entire K-POP industry. Almost everything that is being done now is purely American POP songs literally licked from the West. EXO are one of the very few remaining who personify and preserve the real K-POP while continuing to keep up with the times. EXO music is beyond time and language barriers, so it was, is and will be.

author: @liza_pet
text: EXO is a diamond not only of SM but of the entire K-POP industry. I sincerely apologize, but the visual effects of EXO are too powerful, as soon as they appear on the stage, they capture you with their dazzle, not letting you go until the very end. It's been a whole 11 years, but they simply have no equal in live performances.

author: @liza_pet
